songs.title: Koi Nai
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Kinne Syiaane Munde Ajj kal De
Bheis Badal Ke Naa Mere Chalde
Ajj Ho Ke Khade Kothe Te
Dujjeya Nu Dhikelde Ne Thalle
Main Kinni Waar Duseya
Meinu Samjhda Koi Nai
Mere Naal Vair Pa Ke hun Bachda Koi Nahi
Meri Bandook Hildi Hun Naasda Koi Ni
Laat Ch Goli Lagi Te Bhajda Koi Ni
Mere Variya Di……
Ode Dil Ch Kuj Kuj Hoye Ni
Oda Put Jado Galliyan Ch Ja K
Mere Bare Loka age Jhoota Mootha Bole K
Fer Aake Kehda Koi Nai
Kehda Ina Bachiya Nu Jaan De
Veh Tenu Lok Saare Jaande
Ehna Nu Janda Koi Nai
Veh Tere Charhe aa Naa De
Ehna De Age Piche Koi Nai

[Hook]
Hun Main Kadi Hon Nai Daunga , I'll Be The Only Nigga Hot
Shekhi Taur Nai Main Khedda Mere Lai Koi Vi Nai Rapper
Knne Sare Par Mel Daa Mere Koi Vi Nia Rapper
Knne Sare Par Mel Daa Mere Koi Vi Nia Rapper
